{"tid":1183901,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"冷血主人棄貓何文田街頭 30度高溫下暴曬淋雨","createTime":"2019-06-03T09:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T16:50:49.000Z","uid":175589,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e56846736358960c11ed64bd67c38b359c7a98","tid":1183901,"uid":175589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhgidTz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhgidTz.png&h=7ba68b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24LGbFf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24LGbFf.png&h=015f4a87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzkGbFg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzkGbFg.png&h=c243b844&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjN9kyB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjN9kyB.png&h=0267fc21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/03/173202_7520026f67b6edce57ad56ba99e0c53a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F03%2F173202_7520026f67b6edce57ad56ba99e0c53a.png&h=5a4c42c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飼養寵物是為牠們的一輩子負責任，無論遇到任何問題，棄養都不是唯一解決方法。昨日（2號），有人發現一隻貓咪被棄何文田街頭，連同貓糧﹑貓砂等用品，更在貓袋上貼有「Bring me to home」（帶我回家）的紙條，相信遭主人遺棄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名網民Cindy於「天下貓貓一樣貓」Facebook群組發文，指其女兒在何文田天光道一屋苑前聽到有貓叫聲，發現路邊有一個貓袋，旁邊有糧﹑貓砂，被網民質疑是有計劃地蓄意棄貓。據了解，昨日氣溫最高達攝氏31度，有幾陣大雨，當時正值中午1點多，貓咪被困在一個超細的貓袋中，如同強行暴曬和淋雨，非常殘忍。幸得Cindy女兒及時發現，並將消息發布到Facebook上，網民一呼百應，很快就有人趕到現場救貓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據Cindy接受本報訪問時表示，事發位置人流較少，只是其女兒剛好經過聽到貓叫聲才發現事件。在消息發布後30分鐘內，有四組「貓友」趕到現場，其中一組好心人願意領養，並立即將貓咪帶到獸醫診所作檢查。幸好，驗血報告診斷出貓咪身體健康，並無大礙，被棄原因成疑。被棄貓咪為美國短毛貓，Cindy透露︰「貓咪非常親人，識用頭仔撞人隻手，是乖貓。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件在群組引起極大關注，有700多則回應和200則轉發，更有不少網民大鬧主人狠心︰「棄養已經衰，仲要大熱天時放街邊」﹑「點解可以咁殘忍，一條生命就咁掉喺街，冇人性，會有報應」﹑「出面咁熱，15分鐘都中暑啦」等言論，同時亦感激好心人救起貓咪，祝福貓咪重獲新生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2367812/冷血主人棄貓何文田街頭%2030度高溫下暴曬淋雨\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2367812%2F%E5%86%B7%E8%A1%80%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%A3%84%E8%B2%93%E4%BD%95%E6%96%87%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%252030%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98%E6%BA%AB%E4%B8%8B%E6%9A%B4%E6%9B%AC%E6%B7%8B%E9%9B%A8&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b5b6c03e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2367812/冷血主人棄貓何文田街頭%2030度高溫下暴曬淋雨</a><br />\n<br />\n美短都棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2275817c6d97a3a079aefec1e40fb94215febf","tid":1183901,"uid":9082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bcd3fede7cc501cbd47116e9071da6778d0f24d","tid":1183901,"uid":103559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"018b5adaa7a974c7b1fdc0c831409c5e6bf32d5e","tid":1183901,"uid":119374,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"仆街主人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef671714a2b8a74ae2f05dd1b93f0e1703402bb4","tid":1183901,"uid":11598,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仆街死啦棄養"},{"pid":"d8d7d7a57e6761697c2c2786997f555feba0b749","tid":1183901,"uid":11258,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"支持殘酷對待動物條例"},{"pid":"e545241f299427857072e80fb1d6a2eb0fca8376","tid":1183901,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:41:52.000Z","msg":"幾千銀都冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db57178baa99875f65a4ff0c3cf318bc8bf9363","tid":1183901,"uid":8897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"張紙似唔似小學生嘅功課簿？"},{"pid":"7b662f9fcfaa